<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" class="scroll-smooth">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  
  <title>Stratagem AI: Optimized Operations for Impact – Mark R.</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Stratagem AI diagnoses operational inefficiencies and connects organizations with freelance experts for implementation.">
  
  <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com" defer></script>

  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

  <style>
    /* Minimal custom style for the Inter font */
    body {
      font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    }
  </style>

</head>
<body class="bg-slate-50 text-slate-700 antialiased">

  <main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto my-8 sm:my-12 px-6 sm:px-8 py-10 bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg">
    
    <section class="text-center mb-10">
      <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-slate-800 mb-4">Stratagem AI</h1>
      <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl text-slate-600">Optimized Operations for Measurable Impact</p>
    </section>

    <hr class="my-10 border-slate-200">

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-orange-600 mb-4">The Cost of Inefficiency &amp; Unmet Needs</h2>
      <div class="space-y-4 text-slate-600">
        <p>Many organizations struggle with inefficient internal processes, unclear communication, and under-utilized data. They know they have problems but lack the expertise, time, or resources to identify root causes and implement solutions.</p>
        <p>This leads to wasted resources, missed opportunities, and frustrated teams. These organizations also struggle to find and vet specialized talent for short-term, high-impact projects, leaving critical gaps unaddressed.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <hr class="my-10 border-slate-200">

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-sky-700 mb-4">The Stratagem AI Solution</h2>
      <p class="text-slate-600">Stratagem AI uses advanced analytics to diagnose inefficiencies, generate actionable recommendations, and connect clients with vetted freelance experts for implementation, ensuring measurable impact.</p>
    </section>
    
    <hr class="my-10 border-slate-200">

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-800 text-center mb-8">A Four-Step Path to Excellence</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">

        <div class="bg-slate-100 border border-slate-200 rounded-lg p-6">
          <div class="flex items-center text-sky-800 mb-3">
             <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 mr-3" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z" /></svg>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-lg">1. AI-Powered Diagnostic</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Upload anonymized data; Stratagem AI highlights workflow bottlenecks, communication gaps, and data inefficiencies in intuitive dashboards.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-orange-50 border border-orange-200 rounded-lg p-6">
          <div class="flex items-center text-orange-700 mb-3">
             <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 mr-3" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z" /></svg>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-lg">2. Actionable Recommendations</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Receive a prioritized list of strategic recommendations—from streamlining onboarding to refining communication protocols.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-sky-50 border border-sky-200 rounded-lg p-6">
          <div class="flex items-center text-sky-800 mb-3">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 mr-3" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z" /></svg>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-lg">3. “ImpactBridge” Marketplace</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Get matched with a curated pool of experts in Process Optimization, Data Systems, Strategic Communication, and AI Integration.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-slate-100 border border-slate-200 rounded-lg p-6">
          <div class="flex items-center text-slate-700 mb-3">
             <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 mr-3" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13 7h8m0 0v8m0-8l-8 8-4-4-6 6" /></svg>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-lg">4. Progress Tracking</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Track real-time implementation progress and see KPI improvements—efficiency gains, cost savings, and communication scores.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <hr class="my-10 border-slate-200">

    <section id="interactive-diagnostic">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-orange-600 mb-2">Experience Stratagem AI: Live Diagnostic</h2>
      <p class="text-slate-600 mb-6">Describe an operational inefficiency your organization faces to receive a simulated AI diagnostic and initial recommendation.</p>
      
      <div class="bg-slate-100 border border-slate-200 rounded-lg p-6">
        <textarea
          id="problemInput"
          class="w-full p-3 border border-slate-300 rounded-md shadow-sm focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-sky-500 focus:border-sky-500 transition"
          rows="4"
          placeholder="E.g., 'Our team wastes hours on manual data entry for client onboarding.'"></textarea>

        <button
          id="analyzeBtn"
          class="mt-4 w-full sm:w-auto inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3 bg-sky-600 hover:bg-sky-700 text-white font-bold rounded-md transition-colors focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-sky-500">
          Analyze My Problem
        </button>

        <div id="resultsContainer" class="mt-6" aria-live="polite">
          </div>
      </div>
    </section>

  </main>
  
  <footer class="text-center py-6">
      <p class="text-sm text-slate-500">&copy; 2025 Mark R. Conceptual Design – Stratagem AI</p>
  </footer>

  <script>
    document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {
      const analyzeBtn = document.getElementById('analyzeBtn');
      const problemInput = document.getElementById('problemInput');
      const resultsContainer = document.getElementById('resultsContainer');

      const spinner = `
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center" id="loadingSpinner">
          <div class="animate-spin rounded-full h-8 w-8 border-b-2 border-sky-600"></div>
          <p class="ml-3 text-slate-600">Analyzing patterns...</p>
        </div>
      `;

      analyzeBtn.addEventListener('click', () => {
        const problem = problemInput.value.trim();

        if (problem === '') {
          resultsContainer.innerHTML = `<p class="text-red-600 font-medium">Please describe an inefficiency to analyze.</p>`;
          return;
        }

        // Show spinner
        resultsContainer.innerHTML = spinner;
        
        // Simulate AI analysis delay
        setTimeout(() => {
          // Hide spinner
          const loadingSpinner = document.getElementById('loadingSpinner');
          if (loadingSpinner) loadingSpinner.remove();
          
          // Generate simulated response
          const report = generateReport(problem);
          resultsContainer.innerHTML = report;
          
        }, 2000); // 2-second delay
      });

      function generateReport(problem) {
        // Simple keyword detection for dynamic response
        let primaryFocus = 'Process Optimization';
        let solutionFocus = 'Automating Repetitive Tasks';
        let expertFocus = 'Process Automation Specialist';

        if (problem.toLowerCase().includes('communication') || problem.toLowerCase().includes('meetings')) {
            primaryFocus = 'Communication Workflow';
            solutionFocus = 'Implementing a Centralized Communication Hub';
            expertFocus = 'Strategic Communications Consultant';
        } else if (problem.toLowerCase().includes('data') || problem.toLowerCase().includes('report')) {
            primaryFocus = 'Data Management';
            solutionFocus = 'Creating Automated Reporting Dashboards';
            expertFocus = 'Data Systems Analyst';
        } else if (problem.toLowerCase().includes('onboarding') || problem.toLowerCase().includes('training')) {
            primaryFocus = 'Talent Development';
            solutionFocus = 'Developing a Scalable Digital Onboarding System';
            expertFocus = 'HR & Onboarding Specialist';
        }

        // Return the HTML report template
        return `
          <div class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-lg p-6 animate-fade-in">
            <h4 class="font-bold text-lg text-slate-800 mb-3">Simulated Diagnostic Report</h4>
            
            <div class="space-y-4 text-slate-600 text-sm">
              <p><strong class="font-semibold text-sky-700">Primary Area Detected:</strong> ${primaryFocus}</p>
              <p><strong class="font-semibold text-sky-700">Initial Analysis:</strong> The described issue points to a significant bottleneck in your <strong class="text-slate-800">${primaryFocus.toLowerCase()}</strong>. This often results in lost productivity and can negatively impact team morale or client satisfaction.</p>
              
              <div class="bg-orange-50 border-l-4 border-orange-400 p-4 rounded-r-lg mt-4">
                <p class="font-semibold text-orange-700">Initial Recommendation:</p>
                <p class="text-orange-800">Focus on <strong class="text-slate-800">${solutionFocus}</strong>. By addressing the root cause, you can reclaim significant team hours and improve data accuracy.</p>
              </div>

              <div class="bg-sky-50 border-l-4 border-sky-400 p-4 rounded-r-lg mt-4">
                <p class="font-semibold text-sky-700">Suggested Expert Profile:</p>
                <p class="text-sky-800">Connect with an <strong class="text-slate-800">${expertFocus}</strong> from our marketplace to scope and implement a targeted solution.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <style>
            @keyframes fade-in {
              from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(10px); }
              to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
            }
            .animate-fade-in {
              animation: fade-in 0.5s ease-out forwards;
            }
          </style>
        `;
      }
    });
  </script>

</body>
</html>
